uluscdn.com&oh=00_AYBLTgHTv3oL-BLyreWPNGnR5q7n4ETkCX1B3FnKCuZ3aA&oe=675D60EB"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover Landscape AppLab2.png", "id": "620208195712325", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974672_620208199045658_1632503818660487642_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=is-WYlQ1YygQ7kNvgFnsGhd&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBz9k0ngH2YhUbnyv5Q9nexQEi4SoSyphqwDg-rvtE4gA&oe=675D6108"}, "display_name": "District M", "keywords": [], "long_description": "District M is a VR skater that combines the addictive loop of a rhythm VR game with the madness of a 3rd-person platformer in a stylized festive world.\n\nOur first demo of 2 levels got a lot of love so here\u2019s a new one with 8 test levels that you\u2019ll love even more.\n\nThe game is in development and will launch with 30 levels of increasing difficulty, multiplayer mayhem, gesture-based tricks, magical environments and so much more.\n\nIf you have any feedback/suggestions or face any issue, please ping us on Discord. We really want to build a great game and we can\u2019t do it without your support.\n\nDo join our discord to meet other players, our devs and playtest more of the game till we roll out.\n\nDiscord link: discord.gg/FunVt2Y4wQ\n\nWelcome to District M :)", "short_description": "District M is a VR skater that combines the addictive loop of a rhythm VR game with the madness of a 3rd-person platformer in a stylized festive world.\n\nOur first demo of 2 levels got a lot of love so here\u2019s a new one with 8 test levels that you\u2019ll love even more.\n\nThe game is in development and will launch with 30 levels of increasing difficulty, multiplayer mayhem, gesture-based tricks, magical environments and so much more."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.staging.districtmvr.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "AutoVRse", "support_